data.description: Beautiful 2-year old home on a CUL-DE-SAC in the very popular Cypress Ridge. This home has 4 bedrooms, a bonus room, 3 full baths, fresh paint and updates throughout. With natural light, in the Kitchen and great room. The large island is perfect for entertaining. With plenty of work and cabinet space, the kitchen is a host’s dream! Second floor contains the laundry room, Bonus room, 2 bedrooms, full bath, and Master Suite. Garage has been finished with Premium Modular tile floor. Not only is this house beautiful, the location everything! Sit on your front porch while you watch the neighborhood kids play in the cul-de-sac.  Owner SCREA
